Problem solving:
- fully understand the problem
- modularize the problem into smaller ones
- find a suitable starting point

Concept learning:
- understand the "why" of the concept
- then try to figure to "how" piece by piece making notes
- solve some problems with it
- see if there are alternatives to this method

When reading or watching something:
- try to watch or read the whole thing atleast once to get the holistic view
